'''巴布艾特巴尼-贾巴穆森冲突'''是指一场发生于[[的黎波里_(黎巴嫩)|的黎波里 (黎巴嫩)]]巴布艾特巴尼的[[逊尼派|逊尼派]]穆斯林与贾巴穆森的[[阿拉维派|阿拉维派]]之间爆发的一系列冲突。这两个社区自黎巴嫩内战以来就一直处于对立状态，<ref name=ylib>{{cite news|title=Truce declared in Tripoli between Bab al-Tabbaneh, Jabal Mohsen|url=http://www.yalibnan.com/2012/02/11/truce-declared-in-tripoli-between-bab-al-tabbaneh-jabal-mohsen/|accessdate=27 November 2012|newspaper=Ya Libnan|date=11 February 2012|archive-date=2016-02-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160203053436/http://yalibnan.com/2012/02/11/truce-declared-in-tripoli-between-bab-al-tabbaneh-jabal-mohsen/|dead-url=no}}</ref>并且经常发生冲突。两地的居民因为教派问题以及双方对叙利亚政府的态度而分化。冲突在[[叙利亚内战|叙利亚内战]]期间突然激化。

==背景==
逊尼派穆斯林与阿拉维派穆斯林已经对立了数个世纪。累范特地区的阿拉维派在[[奥斯曼帝国|奥斯曼帝国]]时期遭到打压。但在[[法属叙利亚|法属叙利亚]]时期，阿拉维派通过加入法国殖民地军队获得了地位和影响力。<ref>Mordechai Nisan. ''[http://books.google.dk/books?id=keD9z1XWuNwC&pg=PA118&lpg=PA118&dq=#v=onepage&q&f=false Minorities in the Middle East: a history of struggle and self-expression] {{Wayback|url=http://books.google.dk/books?id=keD9z1XWuNwC&pg=PA118&lpg=PA118&dq=#v=onepage&q&f=false |date=20131104142008 }}''. McFarland, 2002. ISBN 0-7864-1375-1, ISBN 978-0-7864-1375-1</ref>在从法国独立后，叙利亚的阿拉维派掌控权利（这其中以阿萨德家族为代表）。这引起了在叙利亚占多数的逊尼派穆斯林中的一些人的不满。作为回应，这些人在叙利亚发动了逊尼派穆斯林的叛乱活动，叛乱在1982年[[哈马大屠杀|哈马大屠杀]]后被镇压。<ref>{{cite news |last=Shadid |first=Anthony |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2011/04/27/world/middleeast/27syria.html?src=twrhp |title=International Outcry Grows Over Syria Crackdown |work=The New York Times |date=26 April 2011 |accessdate=3 May 2011 |archive-date=2014-01-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140125145158/http://www.nytimes.com/2011/04/27/world/middleeast/27syria.html?src=twrhp |dead-url=no }}</ref>
[[的黎波里|的黎波里]]是拥有50万人口，是黎巴嫩第二大城市，仅次于首都[[贝鲁特|贝鲁特]]。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.asiaone.com/News/AsiaOne+News/World/Story/A1Story20110128-260935.html|title=Sunni camp splits|publisher=Asiaonet|date=|accessdate=2010-01-28|archive-date=2011-02-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110204233445/http://www.asiaone.com/News/AsiaOne%2BNews/World/Story/A1Story20110128-260935.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>由于城内居民中逊尼派占压倒性优势，所以的黎波里被视为黎巴嫩逊尼派保守势力的大本营。从总体上来说，黎巴嫩人口中27%是逊尼派穆斯林。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.state.gov/j/drl/rls/irf/2010/148830.htm |title=Lebanon<!-- Bot generated title --> |accessdate=2014-03-02 |archive-date=2017-11-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171125202930/https://www.state.gov/j/drl/rls/irf/2010/148830.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |author=23 Dec 2008 |url=http://www.atimes.com/atimes/Middle_East/JL23Ak01.html |title=Asia Times Online :: Middle East News, Iraq, Iran current affairs |publisher=Atimes.com |date=2008-12-23 |accessdate=2011-11-14 |archive-date=2018-02-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180221083328/http://www.atimes.com/atimes/Middle_East/JL23Ak01.html |dead-url=no }}</ref> 作为一个逊尼派占主要入口的城市，所有黎巴嫩逊尼派穆斯林派别都集中在的黎波里。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.mafhoum.com/press10/312P1.htm |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2014-03-02 |archive-date=2018-09-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180928122235/http://www.mafhoum.com/press10/312P1.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>大街上挂有很多绘有可兰经的黑色横幅，城内有很多教授逊尼派基本教义的宗教学校，而很多妇女都带面纱出门。的黎波里也是[[黎巴嫩|黎巴嫩]][[萨拉菲主义|萨拉菲主义]]（即逊尼派的原教旨主义）运动的起源地。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www2.alwatan.com.kw/Default.aspx?pageId=84&MgDid=710785|title=Äóîé Áářčçúé|publisher=.alwatan.com.kw|date=|accessdate=2011-11-14|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20111005201730/http://www2.alwatan.com.kw/Default.aspx?pageId=84&MgDid=710785|archivedate=2011-10-05}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.kuwaittimes.net/read_news.php?newsid=MTg3MDI2ODQw |title=» Kuwait Times Website |publisher=Kuwaittimes.net |date= |accessdate=2011-11-14 |archive-date=2012-03-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120324034212/http://www.kuwaittimes.net/read_news.php?newsid=MTg3MDI2ODQw |dead-url=no }}</ref>巴布艾特巴尼社区以及其他的黎巴嫩逊尼派社区与沙特阿拉伯关系密切，沙特向这些社区提供财政支援。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://weekly.ahram.org.eg/2011/1053/re7.htm |title=Al-Ahram Weekly {{!}} Region {{!}} Trial by fire for Lebanon's government<!-- Bot generated title --> |accessdate=2014-03-02 |archive-date=2012-02-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120225012029/http://weekly.ahram.org.eg/2011/1053/re7.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.hughmacleod.co.uk/stormtripoli.htm|title=Tripoli|publisher=Hugh Macleod|date=|accessdate=2010-07-04|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100802044634/http://www.hughmacleod.co.uk/stormtripoli.htm|archivedate=2010-08-02}}</ref>
在黎巴嫩阿拉维派的总人口最多在12万人，将近一半的黎巴嫩阿拉维派教徒居住在的黎波里的贾巴穆森社区以及邻近的Akkar地区的村庄，其中4万至6万名阿拉维派居住在的黎波里。<ref name="mideastmonitor.org">Riad Yazbeck. [http://www.mideastmonitor.org/issues/0808/0808_2.htm#_ftn1 "Return of the Pink Panthers?"] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120219114105/http://www.mideastmonitor.org/issues/0808/0808_2.htm |date=2012-02-19 }}. ''Mideast Monitor''. Vol. 3, No. 2, August 2008</ref> 黎巴嫩的阿拉维派与叙利亚关系密切，其中也包括执政的阿萨德家族。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.nowlebanon.com/NewsArticleDetails.aspx?ID=364329 |title=Lebanon news - NOW Lebanon -Syria Street divides them<!-- Bot generated title --> |access-date=2014-03-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120228114054/http://www.nowlebanon.com/NewsArticleDetails.aspx?ID=364329 |archive-date=2012-02-28 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>
贾巴穆森社区与巴布艾特巴尼社区之间是叙利亚大街，贾巴穆森位于山顶，而巴布艾特巴尼在地势较低的地方。<ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/middle-east/homs-bloodshed-spills-over-into-lebanon-6804804.html | location=London | work=The Independent | first=Robert | last=Fisk | date=2012-02-13 | title=Homs bloodshed spills over into Lebanon | accessdate=2014-03-02 | archive-date=2012-09-06 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120906121612/http://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/middle-east/homs-bloodshed-spills-over-into-lebanon-6804804.html | dead-url=no }}</ref> 这两个社区很多居民都处于失业状态，这使得他们在有冲突发生是能够很容易的被动员起来。黎巴嫩北部地区是黎巴嫩最贫困的地区，长期以来被黎巴嫩政府忽视，这使得极端主义在这一地区有空间发展势力。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://english.al-akhbar.com/node/4158/ |title=Tripoli Clashes: Keeping Conflict Alive {{!}} Al Akhbar English<!-- Bot generated title --> |accessdate=2014-03-02 |archive-date=2014-10-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141022180847/http://english.al-akhbar.com/node/4158/ |dead-url=no }}</ref> North Lebanon is one of the most impoverished parts of Lebanon, and is neglected by the government, leaving room for extremism to grow.<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://english.al-akhbar.com/content/tripoli-north-lebanon-forgotten-city |title=Tripoli, North Lebanon: The Forgotten City {{!}} Al Akhbar English<!-- Bot generated title --> |accessdate=2014-03-02 |archive-date=2014-02-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140204032436/http://english.al-akhbar.com/content/tripoli-north-lebanon-forgotten-city |dead-url=no }}</ref> 这两个社区之前还算是繁荣，直到60年代一场洪水摧毁了很多建筑，之后又爆发了黎巴嫩内战。这一地区之间还留有很多建筑遗迹。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://english.al-akhbar.com/content/illustrious-past-tripoli%E2%80%99s-%E2%80%9Cfrontline%E2%80%9D |title=The Illustrious Past of Tripoli’s "Frontline" {{!}} Al Akhbar English<!-- Bot generated title --> |accessdate=2014-03-02 |archive-date=2012-06-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120628121525/http://english.al-akhbar.com/content/illustrious-past-tripoli%E2%80%99s-%E2%80%9Cfrontline%E2%80%9D |dead-url=no }}</ref>

==黎巴嫩内战期间双方的冲突==
在1975年至1990年的[[黎巴嫩内|黎巴嫩内]]战期间，以贾巴穆森社区为基地的[[阿拉伯民主党|阿拉伯民主党]]与叙利亚结盟，在战斗中与叙利亚政府军并肩作战，在的黎波里对抗主要以巴布艾特巴尼为根据地的塔希德运动（Tawhid Movement）。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.crisisgroup.org/~/media/Files/Middle%20East%20North%20Africa/Iraq%20Syria%20Lebanon/Lebanon/96%20Lebanons%20Politics%20-%20The%20Sunni%20Community%20and%20Hariris%20Future%20Current.ashx |title=LEBANON’S POLITICS: THE SUNNI COMMUNITY AND HARIRI’S FUTURE CURRENT |accessdate=2014-03-02 |archive-date=2013-09-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130927005635/http://www.crisisgroup.org/~/media/Files/Middle%20East%20North%20Africa/Iraq%20Syria%20Lebanon/Lebanon/96%20Lebanons%20Politics%20-%20The%20Sunni%20Community%20and%20Hariris%20Future%20Current.ashx |dead-url=no }}</ref>在开战前，这两个街区的居民都混居在一起。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.crisisgroup.org/en/regions/middle-east-north-africa/egypt-syria-lebanon/lebanon/B29-new-crisis-old-demons-in-lebanon-the-forgotten-lessons-of-bab-tebbaneh-jabal-mohsen.aspx |title=New Crisis, Old Demons in Lebanon: The Forgotten Lessons of Bab-Tebbaneh/Jabal Mohsen - International Crisis Group |publisher=Crisisgroup.org |date=2010-10-14 |accessdate=2012-10-23 |archive-date=2012-12-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121203011259/http://www.crisisgroup.org/en/regions/middle-east-north-africa/egypt-syria-lebanon/lebanon/B29-new-crisis-old-demons-in-lebanon-the-forgotten-lessons-of-bab-tebbaneh-jabal-mohsen.aspx |dead-url=no }}</ref>
1984年8月，塔希德运动与阿拉伯民主党爆发冲突。在的黎波里的街道上双方展开激战，超过400人战死。之后在8月22日，塔希德运动占领了港口区域，使得他们的地位得到加强。双方的战斗持续到9月18日，在叙利亚调解下，冲突双方达成停火协议。<ref>O'Ballance, ''Civil War in Lebanon'' (1998), pp. 146-7.</ref> 到了1985年，塔希德运动基本控制了的黎波里，而阿拉伯民主党只能固守在贾巴穆森。<ref>[http://news.google.com/newspapers?nid=2507&dat=19850928&id=6sBAAAAAIBAJ&sjid=26UMAAAAIBAJ&pg=3993,6860630 The Glasgow Herald - Google News Archive Search<!-- Bot generated title -->]</ref>
1986年12月18日，[[塔希德运动|塔希德运动]]领导人萨米尔•哈桑（Samir al-Hassan）在的黎波里被叙利亚军队逮捕。作为回应。他的手下袭击了一处检查站，导致15名叙利亚士兵丧生。这使得叙利亚政府对塔希德运动忍无可忍。在阿拉伯民主党、[[黎巴嫩共产党|黎巴嫩共产党]]、[[叙利亚社会民族主义党|叙利亚社会民族主义党]]和[[阿拉伯复兴党|阿拉伯复兴党]]民兵的帮助下，叙利亚政府军彻底击败塔希德运动，击毙了大批武装分子，拘捕了有些成员并使该组织残余人员分崩离析。<ref>O'Ballance, ''Civil War in Lebanon'' (1998), p. 171.</ref>

==2008年的冲突==
在2008年黎巴嫩冲突中，亲政府的逊尼派与反政府的阿拉维派发生冲突。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://news.xinhuanet.com/english/2008-09/09/content_9880896.htm |title=North Lebanon reconciliation struck through joint efforts |publisher=News.xinhuanet.com |date=2008-09-09 |accessdate=2011-11-14 |archive-date=2010-06-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100614112223/http://news.xinhuanet.com/english/2008-09/09/content_9880896.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref> 在2007年黎巴嫩冲突后，有迹象显示伊斯兰极端组织“伊斯兰法塔赫”计划袭击的黎波里的阿拉维派，阿拉伯民主党以此为借口重新武装起来。<ref>http://www.mideastmonitor.org/issues/0808/0808_2.htm#_ftn1 {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120219114105/http://www.mideastmonitor.org/issues/0808/0808_2.htm |date=2012-02-19 }}</ref>
在5月10日至11日的夜间，阿拉维派的真主党支持者与逊尼派政府支持者在的黎波里发生激烈冲突。1名妇女在冲突中丧生。<ref>{{cite news|title=Lebanese army sends troops north|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/middle_east/7394395.stm|publisher=''[[BBC|BBC]]''|accessdate=2008-05-16|date=2008-05-11|archive-date=2008-05-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080514142621/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/middle_east/7394395.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref>
5月11日，据报道逊尼派政府支持者使用[[机枪|机枪]]和[[火箭弹|火箭弹]]在阿拉维派为主的贾巴穆森社区与反政府派别的支持者发生战斗。<ref name="BBC May 11">{{cite web |url=http://www.dailystar.com.lb/article.asp?edition_id=1&categ_id=2&article_id=91930 |title=Day 5: Lebanese dare to hope worst is over |publisher=''[[The_Daily_Star_(Lebanon)|The Daily Star (Lebanon)]]'' |accessdate=2008-05-12 |archive-date=2008-05-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080517053917/http://www.dailystar.com.lb/article.asp?edition_id=1&categ_id=2&article_id=91930 |dead-url=no }}</ref> 5月12日，在的黎波里的冲突中有1人丧生，至少6人受伤。<ref name="deadline">{{cite web|title=Lebanon army gives gunmen deadline to disarm|url=http://www.alarabiya.net/articles/2008/05/12/49725.html|publisher=''[[Al_Arabiya|Al Arabiya]]''|accessdate=2008-05-13|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080517143623/http://www.alarabiya.net/articles/2008/05/12/49725.html|archivedate=2008-05-17|deadurl=yes}}</ref>政府军发表声明称如果双方不在次日早晨之前结束冲突，政府军将介入并且在有必要的情况下使用武力结束冲突。
在6月22日和23日，在的黎波里至少有9人—8名平民和1名警察在冲突中丧生，还有55人受伤。冲突在22日早晨6点爆发，双方使用了机枪和火箭弹。<ref>{{cite web|title=Fighting breaks out in northern Lebanon; 4 dead|url=http://origin.mercurynews.com/breakingnews/ci_9665984|author=Bassem Mroue|publisher=''[[Associated_Press|Associated Press]]''|accessdate=2008-09-10}} {{Dead link|date=October 2010|bot=H3llBot}}</ref>
7月25日至29日，23人在的黎波里的冲突中丧生。
9月8日，阿拉维派和逊尼派领导人签署停火协议以结束紧张局势和冲突，这些问题自黎巴嫩内战以来就一直困扰着的黎波里市。<ref>{{cite web|title=Nine killed in sectarian fighting in Lebanon|url=http://www.france24.com/en/20080726-nine-killed-sectarian-fighting-lebanon|publisher=''[[France_24|France 24]]''|accessdate=2008-09-10|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110520125318/http://www.france24.com/en/20080726-nine-killed-sectarian-fighting-lebanon|archivedate=2011年5月20日|deadurl=yes}}</ref>逊尼派的未来阵线领导人萨阿德•哈里里在随后访问了的黎波里并发表声明：“我们两派都是黎巴嫩人，我们不允许任何人试图挑拨我们。我愿做任何我所能做的事以阻止任何人危害到的黎波里市内的阿拉维派的安全，并挫败任何试图危害到阿拉维派乃至整个的黎波里安全的外部阴谋。”<ref>{{cite web|title=Hariri tells Alawites in north Lebanon: We are all Lebanese|url=http://yalibnan.com/site/archives/2008/09/hariri_tells_al.php|publisher=''[[Ya_Libnan|Ya Libnan]]''|accessdate=2008-12-24|archive-date=2008-09-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080912062529/http://yalibnan.com/site/archives/2008/09/hariri_tells_al.php|dead-url=no}}</ref>
