===2011年1月===
2011年1月17日，的黎波里的冲突导致7人丧生，59人受伤。在巴布艾特巴尼的一场支持叙利亚反对派的游行之后冲突发生。冲突双方为来自贾巴穆森和巴布艾特巴尼的武装分子。死者中包括一名黎巴嫩政府军士兵和一名阿拉伯民主党官员。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://studies.aljazeera.net/ResourceGallery/media/Documents/2011/7/28/201172894328667734Lebanon-Perils%20of%20the%20Syrian%20Quake%20Aftershocks.pdf |title=Lebanon... Perils of the Syrian Quake Aftershocks |access-date=2014-03-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121027133752/http://studies.aljazeera.net/ResourceGallery/media/Documents/2011/7/28/201172894328667734Lebanon-Perils%20of%20the%20Syrian%20Quake%20Aftershocks.pdf |archive-date=2012-10-27 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>
===2012年2月===
2012年2月10日至11日，在贾巴穆森和巴布艾特巴尼的冲突导致2到3人丧生。而政府军随后介入了冲突，又导致6名士兵受伤。<ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.nytimes.com/2012/02/16/world/middleeast/syrias-unrest-felt-by-military-in-lebanon.html | work=The New York Times | first=Josh | last=Wood | title=Syria's Unrest Felt by Military in Lebanon | date=2012-02-15 | accessdate=2014-03-02 | archive-date=2014-10-28 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141028082144/http://www.nytimes.com/2012/02/16/world/middleeast/syrias-unrest-felt-by-military-in-lebanon.html | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.aljazeera.com/news/middleeast/2012/02/2012211233556510327.html |title=Syrian violence spills over into Lebanon - Middle East - Al Jazeera English<!-- Bot generated title --> |accessdate=2014-03-02 |archive-date=2018-10-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181002212809/https://www.aljazeera.com/news/middleeast/2012/02/2012211233556510327.html |dead-url=no }}</ref> 人们担心叙利亚内战将会蔓延至黎巴嫩。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.dailystar.com.lb/News/Local-News/2012/Feb-12/162950-2-killed-in-tripoli-violence-mufti-calls-for-arms-free-city.ashx#axzz1mAYOJUqr |title=THE DAILY STAR :: News :: Local News :: Calm returns after 3 die in north Lebanon violence<!-- Bot generated title --> |accessdate=2014-03-02 |archive-date=2014-03-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140302150906/http://www.dailystar.com.lb/News/Local-News/2012/Feb-12/162950-2-killed-in-tripoli-violence-mufti-calls-for-arms-free-city.ashx#axzz1mAYOJUqr |dead-url=no }}</ref>
===2012年5月===
大约2到4人在5月12日夜里的冲突中丧生。<ref name=aj1305>{{Cite web |url=http://www.aljazeera.com/news/middleeast/2012/05/201251383952809563.html |title=Several dead in clashes in Lebanon's Tripoli - Middle East - Al Jazeera English<!-- Bot generated title --> |accessdate=2014-03-02 |archive-date=2018-10-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181002085151/https://www.aljazeera.com/news/middleeast/2012/05/201251383952809563.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=aa1305>{{Cite web |url=http://english.alarabiya.net/articles/2012/05/13/213793.html |title=At least two killed as Alawite-Sunni fighting erupts in Lebanese port city<!-- Bot generated title --> |accessdate=2014-03-02 |archive-date=2017-10-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171012115849/http://english.alarabiya.net/articles/2012/05/13/213793.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=northlebanon>{{Cite web |url=http://www.dailystar.com.lb/News/Local-News/2012/May-13/173210-lebanese-soldier-among-those-killed-in-tripoli-clashes.ashx#axzz1uhec4y59 |title=North Lebanon clashes claim 3, army restores order |accessdate=2014-03-02 |archive-date=2018-11-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181116091915/http://www.dailystar.com.lb/News/Local-News/2012/May-13/173210-lebanese-soldier-among-those-killed-in-tripoli-clashes.ashx#axzz1uhec4y59 |dead-url=no }}</ref>在这场战斗中，双方使用了火箭弹和[[自动步枪|自动步枪]]。<ref name=aa1305/>在冲突爆发前数小时，黎巴嫩政府军与一群年轻的伊斯兰主义者发生交火。当时这群人正在的黎波里举行抗议活动，要求释放一名恐怖分子嫌疑人。<ref name=aa1305/> T冲突是由于当时这群同情叙利亚反对派的年轻人正试图闯入社会民主党的办公室。 据报道，在死者中有3名是逊尼派平民，一名为政府军军官。<ref name=northlebanon/>
冲突持续到了5月14日，最后总共导致5名阿拉维派和1名逊尼派丧生。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.dailystar.com.lb/News/Local-News/2012/May-14/173316-1-killed-10-wounded-in-renewed-fighting-in-north-lebanon.ashx#axzz1uhec4y59 |title=North Lebanon clashes escalate, kill 5 |accessdate=2014-03-02 |archive-date=2018-11-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181116091343/http://www.dailystar.com.lb/News/Local-News/2012/May-14/173316-1-killed-10-wounded-in-renewed-fighting-in-north-lebanon.ashx#axzz1uhec4y59 |dead-url=no }}</ref>
在5月15日，政府军被部署到这一地区并介入到冲突中，导致8人受伤，其中包括1名政府军士兵。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.dailystar.com.lb/News/Local-News/2012/May-16/173584-4-wounded-in-clashes-between-army-gunmen.ashx#axzz1uzBSxwRs |title=THE DAILY STAR :: News :: Local News :: Lebanese soldier among 8 wounded in north Lebanon clashes<!-- Bot generated title --> |accessdate=2014-03-02 |archive-date=2019-06-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190604015034/http://www.dailystar.com.lb/News/Local-News/2012/May-16/173584-4-wounded-in-clashes-between-army-gunmen.ashx#axzz1uzBSxwRs |dead-url=no }}</ref> By 16 May, the clashes had left 11 dead.<ref name=autogenerated1>{{Cite web |url=http://english.al-akhbar.com/content/clashes-resume-tripoli-several-wounded |title=Clashes resume in Tripoli, several wounded {{!}} Al Akhbar English<!-- Bot generated title --> |accessdate=2014-03-02 |archive-date=2017-10-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171019114254/http://english.al-akhbar.com/content/clashes-resume-tripoli-several-wounded |dead-url=no }}</ref>截止5月16日，冲突导致11人丧生，其中包括1名士兵。
来自西方外交官员的消息称这些冲突是一场萨拉菲派革命的序幕，旨在向叙利亚反对派提供帮助。.<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.naharnet.com/stories/en/40721-diplomats-say-salafist-revolution-in-tripoli-aim-at-arming-syrian-opposition |title=Diplomats Say 'Salafist Revolution' in Tripoli Aim at Arming Syrian Opposition — Naharnet<!-- Bot generated title --> |accessdate=2014-03-02 |archive-date=2012-05-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120522050308/http://www.naharnet.com/stories/en/40721-diplomats-say-salafist-revolution-in-tripoli-aim-at-arming-syrian-opposition |dead-url=no }}</ref>由沙特支持的“3月14日联盟”（ March 14 Alliance）指责叙利亚正试图将黎巴嫩拖入危机中。“3月14日联盟”领导人Mustafa Alloush 在一场例行联盟周会之后声称“这事实上是试图将的黎波里变成一个充满恐怖主义的地方，并旨在打击黎巴嫩北部地区，这一地区欢迎并帮助那些来自叙利亚流离失所的难民。”的黎波里及黎巴嫩北部地区在2011年3月叙利亚内乱开始时就有大批叙利亚难民涌入。<ref name=autogenerated1 />
截止5月18日，在5月份的冲突中已有12人丧生，超过100人受伤。.<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.yalibnan.com/2012/05/18/geagea-hezbollah-training-arming-tripoli-groups/#more-39409 |title=Geagea: Hezbollah training, arming Tripoli groups |accessdate=2014-03-02 |archive-date=2012-05-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120520140539/http://www.yalibnan.com/2012/05/18/geagea-hezbollah-training-arming-tripoli-groups/#more-39409 |dead-url=no }}</ref>
5月21日，两个社区之间互射了多枚火箭弹，但没有人员伤亡的报道。5月30日，两个社区间的冲突又导致2人受伤。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.dailystar.com.lb/News/Local-News/2012/May-31/175228-dispute-between-rival-tripoli-residents-wounds-2.ashx#axzz1wAISkDxl |title=THE DAILY STAR :: News :: Local News :: Dispute between rival Tripoli residents wounds 2<!-- Bot generated title --> |accessdate=2014-03-02 |archive-date=2016-02-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160203053436/http://www.dailystar.com.lb/News/Local-News/2012/May-31/175228-dispute-between-rival-tripoli-residents-wounds-2.ashx#axzz1wAISkDxl |dead-url=no }}</ref>
