===2012年6月===
6月2日至3日，贾巴穆森与巴布艾特巴尼之间的冲突导致15人丧生，超过60人受伤。作为对这次战斗的回应，政府军重新开进了分隔了交战双方所在的社区的叙利亚大街，并在冲突双方之间设立了缓冲区。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://english.al-akhbar.com/content/tense-calm-returns-tripoli |title=Tense calm returns to Lebanon's Tripoli |accessdate=2014-03-02 |archive-date=2018-10-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181003020623/https://english.al-akhbar.com/content/tense-calm-returns-tripoli |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.dailystar.com.lb/News/Local-News/2012/Jun-03/175512-fierce-clashes-rage-in-north-lebanon-12-killed.ashx#axzz1wemAxSeY |title=Cautious calm in north Lebanon marred by sporadic shooting |accessdate=2014-03-02 |archive-date=2018-11-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181116092835/http://www.dailystar.com.lb/News/Local-News/2012/Jun-03/175512-fierce-clashes-rage-in-north-lebanon-12-killed.ashx#axzz1wemAxSeY |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.yalibnan.com/2012/06/03/lebanese-army-deployed-in-tripoli-after-15-killed/ |title=Lebanese army deployed in Tripoli after 15 killed |accessdate=2014-03-02 |archive-date=2014-02-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140222064943/http://www.yalibnan.com/2012/06/03/lebanese-army-deployed-in-tripoli-after-15-killed/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.aljazeera.com/news/middleeast/2012/06/201262155357553555.html |title=Many killed as Lebanese clash over Syria |accessdate=2014-03-02 |archive-date=2018-10-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181002210313/https://www.aljazeera.com/news/middleeast/2012/06/201262155357553555.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>  在冲突双方宣布停火之后，在6月3日夜间又发生了多起违反停火的行为，导致1名警察和1名政府军士兵受伤。<ref name=ylib1>{{cite news|title=Several ceasefire violations were reported in Tripoli|url=http://www.yalibnan.com/2012/06/03/several-ceasefire-violations-were-reported-in-tripoli/|accessdate=27 November 2012|newspaper=Ya Libnan|date=3 June 2012|archive-date=2019-06-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190604185054/http://yalibnan.com/2012/06/03/several-ceasefire-violations-were-reported-in-tripoli/|dead-url=no}}</ref>6月8日，在贾巴穆森1人被狙击手打死。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.dailystar.com.lb/News/Local-News/2012/Jun-08/176185-one-killed-one-wounded-by-sniper-fire-in-north-lebanon.ashx#axzz1xD3cM9cT |title=The Daily Star: One killed, one wounded by sniper fire in north Lebanon<!-- Bot generated title --> |accessdate=2014-03-02 |archive-date=2016-02-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160203053436/http://www.dailystar.com.lb/News/Local-News/2012/Jun-08/176185-one-killed-one-wounded-by-sniper-fire-in-north-lebanon.ashx#axzz1xD3cM9cT |dead-url=no }}</ref>
