===2012年7月===
7月18日，在巴布艾特巴尼的一场庆祝多名叙利亚部长遭到炸弹袭击的反叙利亚活动中，1人因流弹丧生，多人受伤。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.naharnet.com/stories/en/47044-one-killed-in-tripoli-by-gunshots-fired-in-celebration-of-damascus-bombing |title=One Killed in Tripoli by Gunshots Fired in Celebration of Damascus Bombing — Naharnet<!-- Bot generated title --> |accessdate=2014-03-02 |archive-date=2018-10-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181005210107/http://www.naharnet.com/stories/en/47044-one-killed-in-tripoli-by-gunshots-fired-in-celebration-of-damascus-bombing |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://english.al-akhbar.com/content/one-dead-lebanon-after-anti-assad-celebrations |title=One dead in Lebanon after anti-Assad celebrations {{!}} Al Akhbar English<!-- Bot generated title --> |accessdate=2014-03-02 |archive-date=2018-10-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181003013723/https://english.al-akhbar.com/content/one-dead-lebanon-after-anti-assad-celebrations |dead-url=no }}</ref>
7月21日，由于非政治上的原因，两个巴布艾特巴尼的逊尼派家族成员发生冲突，导致2人丧生，多人受伤。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.dailystar.com.lb/News/Local-News/2012/Jul-22/181510-two-killed-7-wounded-in-north-lebanon-family-dispute.ashx#axzz20Ua220bI |title=THE DAILY STAR :: News :: Local News :: Two killed, 7 wounded in north Lebanon family dispute<!-- Bot generated title --> |accessdate=2014-03-02 |archive-date=2014-03-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140302150902/http://www.dailystar.com.lb/News/Local-News/2012/Jul-22/181510-two-killed-7-wounded-in-north-lebanon-family-dispute.ashx#axzz20Ua220bI |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.naharnet.com/stories/en/47358-one-killed-as-personal-dispute-escalates-into-armed-clash-in-bab-al-tabbaneh |title=One Killed as Personal Dispute Escalates into Armed Clash in Bab al-Tabbaneh — Naharnet<!-- Bot generated title --> |accessdate=2014-03-02 |archive-date=2014-03-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140302151342/http://www.naharnet.com/stories/en/47358-one-killed-as-personal-dispute-escalates-into-armed-clash-in-bab-al-tabbaneh |dead-url=no }}</ref>在7月29日，又有2人因此次冲突丧生。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.naharnet.com/stories/en/48251-2-dead-4-hurt-as-families-dispute-erupts-into-gunfire-in-bab-al-tabbaneh |title=2 Dead, 5 Hurt as Families Dispute Erupts into Gunfire in Bab al-Tabbaneh — Naharnet<!-- Bot generated title --> |accessdate=2014-03-02 |archive-date=2014-03-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140302150830/http://www.naharnet.com/stories/en/48251-2-dead-4-hurt-as-families-dispute-erupts-into-gunfire-in-bab-al-tabbaneh |dead-url=no }}</ref>
7月27日，有两人在返回位于贾巴穆森社区的途中遭到不明身份袭击者的刺死。这起袭击事件引起了武装分子之间的冲突，<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.naharnet.com/stories/en/48076-fighting-erupts-in-rival-tripoli-districts-army-hits-back-at-shooters |title=Fighting Erupts in Rival Tripoli Districts, Army Hits Back at Shooters — Naharnet<!-- Bot generated title --> |accessdate=2014-03-02 |archive-date=2018-10-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181005210039/http://www.naharnet.com/stories/en/48076-fighting-erupts-in-rival-tripoli-districts-army-hits-back-at-shooters |dead-url=no }}</ref> 造成15人受伤，其中包括3名政府军士兵。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://english.al-akhbar.com/content/three-lebanese-soldiers-wounded-fresh-tripoli-clashes |title=Three Lebanese soldiers wounded in fresh Tripoli clashes {{!}} Al Akhbar English<!-- Bot generated title --> |accessdate=2014-03-02 |archive-date=2018-10-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181003015923/https://english.al-akhbar.com/content/three-lebanese-soldiers-wounded-fresh-tripoli-clashes |dead-url=no }}</ref>
===2012年8月===
2012年8月9日，来自Tawheed运动的支持真主党的逊尼派人士与萨拉菲主义者在的黎波里发生冲突。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.dailystar.com.lb/News/Local-News/2012/Aug-09/183932-hezbollah-ally-camps-out-in-mosque-after-tripoli-clashes.ashx#axzz234YADSXf |title=The Daily Star: Hezbollah ally camps out in mosque after Tripoli clashes<!-- Bot generated title --> |accessdate=2014-03-02 |archive-date=2019-06-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190608213947/http://www.dailystar.com.lb/News/Local-News/2012/Aug-09/183932-hezbollah-ally-camps-out-in-mosque-after-tripoli-clashes.ashx#axzz234YADSXf |dead-url=no }}</ref>
8月20日至21日，根据黎巴嫩安全部队和医疗机构的消息，在的黎波里逊尼派穆斯林与阿拉维派的冲突导致12人丧生，超过100人受伤，其中包括15名政府军士兵。两名死者来自贾巴穆森社区，5人来自巴布艾特巴尼。在死者中有一名年仅13岁的男孩。在政府军受伤人员中有5人是在8月20日的枪战中受伤，还有5人是在次日一起针对一处政府军检查站的[[手榴弹|手榴弹]]袭击事件中受伤。<ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2012/08/21/us-lebanon-tripoli-idUSBRE87K0FC20120821 | work=Reuters | title=Fighting in Lebanese city for second night, 7 killed | date=21 August 2012 | accessdate=2014-03-02 | archive-date=2012-08-25 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120825064410/http://www.reuters.com/article/2012/08/21/us-lebanon-tripoli-idUSBRE87K0FC20120821 | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>[http://www.trust.org/alertnet/news/fighting-in-lebanese-city-for-second-night-7-killed/ Fighting in Lebanese city for second night, 7 killed (Reuters)] {{webarchive|url=https://archive.is/20130416000357/http://www.trust.org/alertnet/news/fighting-in-lebanese-city-for-second-night-7-killed/ |date=2013-04-16 }}</ref>
8月22日，黎巴嫩政府军再次尝试阻止暴力冲突发生。政府军向长期有冲突的社区派遣了部队。但是，政府军遭遇严重损失，并被迫撤退。在与社区领导人进行对话后，政府军成功使得冲突双方达成停火。
但停火在8月23日以失败告终，在全城范围内爆发了新的一系列冲突。黎巴嫩政府军向街道内部署了坦克以试图再次控制局势。
8月24日，在当天黎明Qobbah和 贾巴穆森街区逊尼派和阿拉维派武装分子使用轻武器和火箭弹展开交火，逊尼派神职人员Sheikh Khaled al Barade在冲突中被狙击手枪杀。据报道Sheikh Khaled al Barade是一伙逊尼派伊斯兰武装分子的首领，他的死导致城内发生新的教派骚乱，战斗也因此进一步升级。在逊尼派社区至少有7座阿拉维派群众的商铺遭到不明身份的袭击者焚毁。在持续一天的战斗中有两名新闻记者受伤，据报道至少有3人丧生，21人受伤。<ref name=BBC24AugustClericKilled>{{cite news|title=Sunni cleric killed in north Lebanon clashes|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-middle-east-19366256|accessdate=24 August 2012|date=24 August 2012|agency=BBC News|archive-date=2012-08-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120824113127/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-middle-east-19366256|dead-url=no}}</ref> 
据统计，这一轮冲突共导致17人丧生，超过120人受伤。
===2012年10月===
10月21日，黎巴嫩安全部队情报局长维萨姆•哈桑遭暗杀引发了暴力冲突。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.aljazeera.com/news/middleeast/2012/10/20121020501561664.html |title=Syria blamed for deadly Lebanon blast - Middle East |publisher=Al Jazeera English |date=20 October 2010 |accessdate=2012-10-23 |archive-date=2018-10-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181002211023/https://www.aljazeera.com/news/middleeast/2012/10/20121020501561664.html |dead-url=no }}</ref> 在贾巴穆森与巴布艾特巴尼两个社区间的冲突中两名小女孩和一名男子丧生。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.dailystar.com.lb/News/Local-News/2012/Oct-22/192271-three-dead-in-tripoli-clashes-arrests-made.ashx#axzz29z9qZY9N |title=Three dead in Tripoli clashes, arrests made |publisher=The Daily Star |date=2012-08-27 |accessdate=2012-10-23 |archive-date=2018-11-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181116091332/http://www.dailystar.com.lb/News/Local-News/2012/Oct-22/192271-three-dead-in-tripoli-clashes-arrests-made.ashx#axzz29z9qZY9N |dead-url=no }}</ref>当天晚上，在贝鲁特Tariq al-Jadeedah社区前总理哈里里的拥护者与敌对派别发生冲突。10月22日， 2名逊尼派和1名阿拉维派在冲突中丧生，另有15人受伤。<ref>{{cite news |last=Holmes |first=Oliver |url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2012/10/23/us-lebanon-crisis-idUSBRE89L0CK20121023 |title=Fighting flares in Lebanese city over Syria loyalties |publisher=Reuters |date=23 October 2012 |accessdate=2012-10-23 |archive-date=2012-10-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121023234225/http://www.reuters.com/article/2012/10/23/us-lebanon-crisis-idUSBRE89L0CK20121023 |dead-url=no }}</ref>
===2012年12月===
2012年12月4日至9日，在的黎波里的冲突至少造成12人丧生，73人受伤。这起冲突是由之前Tall Kalakh伏击所引发的，冲突双方为阿拉维派和逊尼派。当时来自黎巴嫩北部的大约14到20名伊斯兰主义者（其中包括1名巴勒斯坦人）在叙黎边境的Tall Kalakh遭到伏击并被击毙。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.aljazeera.com/news/middleeast/2012/12/2012124152513238762.html |title=Fatal sectarian clashes in Lebanon’s Tripoli |accessdate=2014-03-02 |archive-date=2018-10-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181002214746/https://www.aljazeera.com/news/middleeast/2012/12/2012124152513238762.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.aljazeera.com/news/middleeast/2012/12/2012125145553286195.html |title=(Al Jazeera) |accessdate=2014-03-02 |archive-date=2019-04-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190402114120/https://www.aljazeera.com/news/middleeast/2012/12/2012125145553286195.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>这些人是准备前往叙利亚加入反对派的。
===2013年的冲突===
2月28日，有5人因为向这两个社区投掷手榴弹而被捕。他们声称受一个代号“Z.S.”的人的指使，意图制造混乱。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.naharnet.com/stories/en/73730-army-arrests-suspect-for-tossing-grenades-in-tripoli-to-incite-strife |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2014-03-02 |archive-date=2014-03-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140302145132/http://www.naharnet.com/stories/en/73730-army-arrests-suspect-for-tossing-grenades-in-tripoli-to-incite-strife |dead-url=no }}</ref> 
在3月，在贾巴穆森和巴布艾特巴尼之间发生了一些零星冲突。在贾巴穆森有两人被狙击手开枪打伤。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.naharnet.com/stories/en/76000-two-hurt-by-sniper-fire-in-jabal-mohsen-as-cautious-calm-engulfs-tripoli |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2014-03-02 |archive-date=2014-03-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140302145727/http://www.naharnet.com/stories/en/76000-two-hurt-by-sniper-fire-in-jabal-mohsen-as-cautious-calm-engulfs-tripoli |dead-url=no }}</ref>3天之后，一名来自贾巴穆森的男子遭枪击身亡。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.naharnet.com/stories/en/76377-one-killed-in-tripoli-clashes-after-shooting-erupts-at-hospital |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2014-03-02 |archive-date=2014-03-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140302151844/http://www.naharnet.com/stories/en/76377-one-killed-in-tripoli-clashes-after-shooting-erupts-at-hospital |dead-url=no }}</ref>
截止3月22日，有6人（其中包括一名政府军士兵）死于冲突。在3月23日，又有3人在冲突中丧生。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.naharnet.com/stories/en/76713-3-dead-1-hurt-in-fresh-clashes-between-bab-al-tabbaneh-jabal-mohsen |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2014-03-02 |archive-date=2014-03-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140302144623/http://www.naharnet.com/stories/en/76713-3-dead-1-hurt-in-fresh-clashes-between-bab-al-tabbaneh-jabal-mohsen |dead-url=no }}</ref>
在5月19日至20日，在贾巴穆森和巴布艾特巴尼之间新的冲突造成2名平民和2名政府军丧生。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.naharnet.com/stories/en/83651-two-soldiers-killed-as-army-seeks-to-contain-ongoing-tripoli-clashes |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2014-03-02 |archive-date=2018-12-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181221200640/http://www.naharnet.com/stories/en/83651-two-soldiers-killed-as-army-seeks-to-contain-ongoing-tripoli-clashes |dead-url=no }}</ref> 到22日，有12日在5月份的冲突中丧生。在成为袭击对象后，黎巴嫩政府军在5月23日撤离了该市街道。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://english.al-akhbar.com/content/lebanese-army-pulls-out-tripolis-streets |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2014-03-02 |archive-date=2018-10-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181003053647/https://english.al-akhbar.com/content/lebanese-army-pulls-out-tripolis-streets |dead-url=no }}</ref>在当天夜里的冲突中，6人丧生，而迫击炮第一次在冲突中被使用。截止5月26日，31人在冲突中丧生， 204人受伤。之后贾巴穆森社区遭到政府军的搜查，而阿拉伯民主党领导人Rifa'at Eid则对此表示怀疑，因为敌对的巴布艾特巴尼社区并没有遭到突击搜查。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.naharnet.com/stories/en/85631-army-starts-removing-jabal-mohsen-barricades-eid-voices-reservation-and-kabbara-gives-48-hour-ultimatum |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2014-03-02 |archive-date=2018-12-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181221200709/http://www.naharnet.com/stories/en/85631-army-starts-removing-jabal-mohsen-barricades-eid-voices-reservation-and-kabbara-gives-48-hour-ultimatum |dead-url=no }}</ref>
11月29日至30日，有13人在冲突中丧生。

